lead_paragraph: Red Bull's Max Verstappen kept Mercedes off the top of the timesheets in final practice for the Mexican Grand Prix on Saturday, with Lewis Hamilton second fastest and championship leader Nico Rosberg fourth.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: Verstappen Fastest in Final Mexico Practice
